#Timezone Syn
To ensure the clock synchronization all the machine must share the same time zone. 
In this case the America/Sao_Paulo timezone.
**$sudo timedatectl set-timezone America/Sao_Paulo**

#Commom user
All the three machines must have one user in commom. To add a new user named krbuser on the system:
**$sudo adduser krbuser**
And complete the asked informations.
